{% doc %}
  @prompt
    "Create a customer testimonial section with the same structure and layout as the reference design.
    Section Layout & Structure:
    Title Section:
    Use <h2> tag for heading.
    Text: What Customers Are <span>Saying</span> After Trying Resilia.
    Word inside <span> (Saying) should be styled in orange.
    Fully editable title text.
    Description Section:
    3 lines of editable description text under the title.
    Center aligned, standard readable font size.
    Testimonial Cards (3 columns):
    3 equal-width columns in a row (responsive → collapse into single column on mobile).
    Each column styled as a card:
    Light background, thin green border, rounded corners.
    First part: 3–4 lines of editable customer testimonial (quote).
    Second part (footer):
    Small logo/icon (green check icon by default, fully replaceable).
    Customer name + age in bold.
    Second line with "Verified Customer" label in smaller text.
    CTA Button:
    Full-width button below testimonials.
    Background: orange.
    Text: TRY RESILIA RISK-FREE (editable).
    Rounded corners, bold white text.
    Hover effect: darker orange.
    Design & Styling:
    Title: bold, with highlighted <span> word in orange.
    Testimonials: cards evenly spaced with equal padding, green borders, light background.
    Text inside cards: testimonial quote italic or styled to stand out.
    Verified Customer info: smaller, aligned left inside card.
    Button: centered, full width, strong call-to-action style.
    Responsive Behavior:
    On desktop: 3 columns side by side.
    On mobile: collapses to single column stacked vertically.
    Customization Options:
    All text editable (title, description, testimonials, button).
    Colors (orange, green, white, black) fully customizable.
    Icons replaceable (upload SVG/PNG).
    Number of testimonials adjustable (add/remove columns).
    CTA button text, color, and link fully editable.
    Deliver as a responsive Shopify section with full editing flexibility, matching the reference design exactly.

{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-testimonials-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 0px 20px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.section_background_color }};
  }
div#shopify-block-ASm1IUmNuUVFZYitXL__ai_gen_block_e7b2981_nU84Kd {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 726px;
    margin: 0 auto;
}
  .ai-testimonials-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
   
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .ai-testimonials-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.title_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: {{ block.settings.title_color }};
    margin: 0 0 20px 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .ai-testimonials-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} strong {
    color: {{ block.settings.highlight_color }};
  }

  .ai-testimonials-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.description_font_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.description_color }};
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .ai-testimonials-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .ai-testimonial-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_background_color }};
    border: {{ block.settings.card_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.card_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    padding: 15px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    min-height: 200px;
  }

  .ai-testimonial-quote-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.quote_font_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.quote_color }};
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .ai-testimonial-footer-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .ai-testimonial-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .ai-testimonial-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .ai-testimonial-icon-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_border_color }};
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ai-testimonial-icon-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 60%;
    height: 60%;
    fill: {{ block.settings.highlight_color }};
  }

  .ai-testimonial-customer-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .ai-testimonial-name-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.name_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: {{ block.settings.name_color }};
    margin: 0 0 4px 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .ai-testimonial-verified-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.verified_font_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.verified_color }};
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .ai-testimonials-cta-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ai-testimonials-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 18px 40px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_background_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_text_color }};
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.button_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: bold;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.button_border_radius }}px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .ai-testimonials-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_color }};
    color:#ee882f;
    border:1px solid #ee882f;
  }

